    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Oracle XStream CDC — Throughput & Performance\n\nPipeline: Oracle → XStream → Kafka Connect → Kafka topics.\n\n**If panels show 0 / “No data” while Connect producer bytes move:** topic names or broker JMX may not match the variables. Set **`cdc_topic_full`** to the **exact** Kafka topic (Explore: `kafka_server_brokertopicmetrics_messagesin_total` and read the `topic` label). PDB-prefixed topics look like `racdb.XSTRPDB.ORDERMGMT.MTX_TRANSACTION_ITEMS`.\n\n**Bytes In panel:** needs per-topic broker JMX (`kafka_server_brokertopicmetrics_bytesin_*`). If **rate** is empty, the panel also plots **OneMinuteRate** fallbacks.\n\n**Series “Oracle Capture”** needs `oracle_xstream_capture_*` from an Oracle exporter; adjust **Oracle exporter job** or deploy the exporter.\n\n**Datasource:** pick **`DS_PROMETHEUS`** that scrapes `kafka-broker` / `kafka-connect`."
      },
      "title": "Dashboard Overview",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "id": 10,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Key Performance Indicators (Current)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "red", "value": null }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.1 }, { "color": "green", "value": 1 }] },
          "unit": "ops",
          "decimals": 2
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 11,
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "justifyMode": "auto", "orientation": "auto", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "value_and_name" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(kafka_server_brokertopicmetrics_messagesin_total{job=~\"$broker_job\",topic=\"$cdc_topic_full\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Broker → $cdc_topic_full (msg/s)",
          "refId": "Z"
        },
        {
          "expr": "kafka_connect_source_task_metrics_source_record_write_rate{job=~\"$connect_job\",connector=~\"oracle-xstream.*\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{connector}} t{{task}}",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(kafka_producer_record_send_rate{job=~\"$connect_job\"})",
          "legendFormat": "producer send (sum, fallback)",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(debezium_oracle_connector_total_number_of_events_seen{job=~\"$connect_job\",context=\"streaming\"}[5m])) by (server)",
          "legendFormat": "Debezium events/s {{server}}",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "description": "Source-task rate, producer fallback, Debezium event rate (Oracle connector).",
      "title": "Current Connector Throughput (rec/s)",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
